31 (3) THE REGISTERED CARDIOVASCULAR INVASIVE SPECIALIST HAS
32 COMPLETED THE TRAINING AND EDUCATION AND HAS THE EXPERIENCE REQUIRED
33 BY REGULATIONS ADOPTED BY THE BOARD; AND

